import React from 'react';

export default class Cadastro extends React.Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <fieldset>
        <form>
          <label>
            Nome:
            <input type="text" />
          </label>
          <label>
            E-mail:
            <input type="email" />
          </label>
          <label>
            Idade:
            <input type="number" />
          </label>
          <label>
            Senha:
            <input type="password" />
          </label>
        </form>
      </fieldset>
    );
  }
}
